": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/fa3a0431ee232cdeeccd0608eb5aed21?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/fa3a0431ee232cdeeccd0608eb5aed21?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/fa3a0431ee232cdeeccd0608eb5aed21?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1534149980, "last_modified": 1534149980}, "last_reply_by": "wclebb", "last_touched": 1730952143, "title": "广东真的太热了，不利于创作", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1087269", "created": 1730927361, "deleted": 0, "content": "今天立冬，广东还开着空调入睡。\r\n\r\n炎热的天气，周期又长，让人心情烦闷，不利于编程、自媒体等创作型工作。\r\n\r\n而且珠三角房价实在不低。我这买一套新房 300 万起步（三室）。\r\n\r\n如果不考虑家庭（没有家庭当然很爽了，孤独除外），数字移民生活实在不错的。\r\n\r\n比如云贵那边，天气好，消费又不高，小地方节奏也慢。\r\n\r\n就算租房住，一年生活花费 10 来万，300 万（还不算买房利息）可以租 30 年了。\r\n\r\n虽然没体验过这种生活，但是心有向往之。大佬们怎么看？", "content_rendered": "<p>今天立冬，广东还开着空调入睡。</p>\n<p>炎热的天气，周期又长，让人心情烦闷，不利于编程、自媒体等创作型工作。</p>\n<p>而且珠三角房价实在不低。我这买一套新房 300 万起步（三室）。</p>\n<p>如果不考虑家庭（没有家庭当然很爽了，孤独除外），数字移民生活实在不错的。</p>\n<p>比如云贵那边，天气好，消费又不高，小地方节奏也慢。</p>\n<p>就算租房住，一年生活花费 10 来万，300 万（还不算买房利息）可以租 30 年了。</p>\n<p>虽然没体验过这种生活，但是心有向往之。大佬们怎么看？</p>\n", "last_modified": 1730927361, "replies": 62, "id": 1087269}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_large.png?m=1608969785", "name": "life", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_normal.png?m=1608969785", "title": "生活", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/life", "topics": 6579, "footer": "", "header": "生活中的技术讨论", "title_alternative": "Life", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_mini.png?m=1608969785", "stars": 1588, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 557, "parent_node_name": ""}, "member": {"id": 87080, "username": "ysicing", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/ysicing", "website": "https://ysicing.me", "twitter": "", "psn": "", "github": "ysicing", "btc": "", "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/cba2/dc20/87080_mini.png?m=1711724354", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/cba2/dc20/87080_normal.png?m=1711724354", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/cba2/dc20/87080_large.png?m=1711724354", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/cba2/dc20/87080_xlarge.png?m=1711724354", "avatar_xxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/cba2/dc20/87080_xlarge.png?m=1711724354", "created": 1418791798, "last_modified": 1711724354}, "last_reply_by": "xu455255849", "last_touched": 1730951821, "title": "大家选袜子会仔细去挑么", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1087119", "created": 1730873398, "deleted": 0, "content": "如题。\r\n\r\n冬天来了，冬袜也得好好挑一挑😂，保暖穿得舒服。\r\n\r\n请问，大家都怎么挑的😂。", "content_rendered": "<p>如题。</p>\n<p>冬天来了，冬袜也得好好挑一挑😂，保暖穿得舒服。</p>\n<p>请问，大家都怎么挑的😂。</p>\n", "last_modified": 1730873398, "replies": 54, "id": 1087119}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/3cef/96dc/949_large.png?m=1730363795", "name": "nas", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/3cef/96dc/949_normal.png?m=1730363795", "title": "NAS", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/nas", "topics": 2308, "footer": "", "header": "关于网络存储设备的讨论", "title_alternative": "NAS", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/3cef/96dc/949_mini.png?m=1730363795", "stars": 2482, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 949, "parent_node_name": "hardware"}, "member": {"id": 598011, "username": "wowy", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/wowy", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/49d0aff00f21bbc50c0bb2ed6dd8ffc7?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/49d0aff00f21bbc50c0bb2ed6dd8ffc7?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/49d0aff00f21bbc50c0bb2ed6dd8ffc7?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1666151315, "last_modified": 1718179719}, "last_reply_by": "jackerbauer", "last_touched": 1730951278, "title": "mac mini m4 All In One 求助", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1087153", "created": 1730879201, "deleted": 0, "content": "求助，想搭建一个家庭服务器，目前心仪的机器是新出的 mac mini M4.大致的需求有以下几个。\r\n1. 外网 remote ssh 访问。使用系统包含 windows mac 。\r\n2. 外网远程桌面访问，使用系统包含 windows mac 。\r\n3. 挂载 PT ，用作电影服务，给家里电视播放用。\r\n4. 搭建音乐服务。使用系统包含 windows mac iphone android 。\r\n5. 文件备份，把手机的照片什么的备份到电脑中。\r\n6. mac mini 平时居家也需要保证正常使用。\r\n7. mac mini 需要挂移动硬盘，自带的硬盘估计不够用，并且加量太贵了。\r\n\r\n想请教下，要达成这几个要求具体要怎么做比较合适。", "content_rendered": "<p>求助，想搭建一个家庭服务器，目前心仪的机器是新出的 mac mini M4.大致的需求有以下几个。</p>\n<ol>\n<li>外网 remote ssh 访问。使用系统包含 windows mac 。</li>\n<li>外网远程桌面访问，使用系统包含 windows mac 。</li>\n<li>挂载 PT ，用作电影服务，给家里电视播放用。</li>\n<li>搭建音乐服务。使用系统包含 windows mac iphone android 。</li>\n<li>文件备份，把手机的照片什么的备份到电脑中。</li>\n<li>mac mini 平时居家也需要保证正常使用。</li>\n<li>mac mini 需要挂移动硬盘，自带的硬盘估计不够用，并且加量太贵了。</li>\n</ol>\n<p>想请教下，要达成这几个要求具体要怎么做比较合适。</p>\n", "last_modified": 1730879201, "replies": 54, "id": 1087153}]